body_html:
Hi Alexa, thanks for the report.

We're trying to clean out the api_guides/ directory. Everything in there was out-dated.

It looks like we were a little over-zealous.
These broken links will all be deleted when we publish r1.12. In a few days.

I'm going to close this, because I believe there is no further work to do on it. But please re-open if it's still broken after the r1.12 release.

Thanks.
